_sText:
This map closley resembles the classic 1corridoor format. 
This map has two parralel corridoors with a crossover point at each spawn to switch between the two.
Each secion of the corridoor is seperated by real style doors, rather than the vertical sliding ones seen in the old 1corridoors.

***!!!UPDATES!!!***
After the Beta Release of this map, certain issues have been raised and now fixed.

-Spawn points verified allowing more than 5 players!
-Rooms optimised and de-cluttered
-Steps in one of the room removed due to Navigation difficulties
-CCTV cam in CT spawn Fixed
-Sounds fixed
-Buttons Fixed
